data.value:
Version 2.1.1 -Added new bucket tool - easily change the background to any colour you desire -Added new guides to the help tab - check them out if you have an issue
Version 2.0.1 -New Highlighter Tool -New Triangle Tool - click in 3 places where you want the triangle's corners to be -Colors are now available for all tools -All shape tools can now be filled
Version 1.2.1 -Fancy new loading screen -New Version History tab - be informed of the latest and greatest updates! -Rectangle and Ellipse Tools work in all directions now -Various other bug fixes and optimizations
